Subject: [PATCH v5 13/25] drm/msm: Compute dumb-buffer sizes with drm_mode_size_dumb()
Date: Fri, 13 Jun 2025 11:00:32 +0200
Message-ID: <20250613090431.127087-14-tzimmermann@suse.de>
